                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 17.266,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 97740,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in 73-1316, Renegotiation Board against Grumman and 73-1233, Labor Board against Sears will be announced by Mr. Justice White."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 17.266,
